When you need to search the Context Engine knowledge graph, discover what an entity is connected to, or triage/resolve CVEs, use the `ctx-cli` CLI rather than guessing from training data. See the `ctx` skill — `codebase-search.md` for search and graph traversal, `security.md` for the CVE inbox with ready-to-apply fix diffs.
